{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"wvih6jmvz02pj960ufl1h6b","title":"Stokes Theorem","desc":"","updated":1657010186216,"created":1657007830412,"custom":{},"fname":"science.math.calculus.Stokes Theorem","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"c55d2411e1bf486eb68289082b01345f","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"science.math.calculus.Stokes Theorem","id":"wvih6jmvz02pj960ufl1h6b","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"science.math.calculus.Fundamental Theorem of Calculus","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":27,"offset":147},"end":{"line":7,"column":84,"offset":204},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"science.math.calculus.Fundamental Theorem of Calculus"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"science.math.calculus.Stokes Theorem","id":"wvih6jmvz02pj960ufl1h6b","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"science.math.calculus.Green's Theorem","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":89,"offset":209},"end":{"line":7,"column":130,"offset":250},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"science.math.calculus.Green's Theorem"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"science.math.calculus.Stokes Theorem","id":"wvih6jmvz02pj960ufl1h6b","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"science.math.calculus.Conservative Forces","position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":1,"offset":1164},"end":{"line":52,"column":46,"offset":1209},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"science.math.calculus.Conservative Forces"}},{"from":{"fname":"science.math.calculus.Green's Theorem","id":"jbgt0x761z1ee870xvcygmx","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":3,"offset":1413},"end":{"line":50,"column":43,"offset":1453},"indent":[]},"value":"science.math.calculus.Stokes Theorem"}],"anchors":{"stokes-theorem":{"type":"header","text":"Stokes Theorem","value":"stokes-theorem","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"motivation-and-heuristic":{"type":"header","text":"Motivation and Heuristic","value":"motivation-and-heuristic","line":16,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"ARgyj1BpfDeaSTLzKqXnf","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"stokes-theorem\">Stokes Theorem<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#stokes-theorem\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"stokes-theorem-1\">Stokes Theorem<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#stokes-theorem-1\"></a></h1>\n<p>Connects an integral over <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span></span> dimensional region to an integral over an <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">n-1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6667em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></span> dimensional boundary.</p>\n<p>Includes as special cases <a href=\"/PublicPersonalKnowledgeBase/notes/746u9udpsdr616cfqgdmx0d\">Fundamental Theorem of Calculus</a> and <a href=\"/PublicPersonalKnowledgeBase/notes/jbgt0x761z1ee870xvcygmx\">Green's Theorem</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"motivation-and-heuristic\">Motivation and Heuristic<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#motivation-and-heuristic\"></a></h2>\n<p>Now, imagine we want to calculate the integral <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mo>∫</mo><mi>C</mi></msub><mi>F</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\int_C F\\cdot n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.1608em;vertical-align:-0.3558em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\"><span class=\"mop op-symbol small-op\" style=\"margin-right:0.19445em;position:relative;top:-0.0006em;\">∫</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1225em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.3442em;margin-left:-0.1945em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3558em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span></span></span></span></span>. Call this a 'circulation' across the boundary <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span></span></span></span></span>.</p>\n<p>Now, we can see that if we 'cut up' C into pieces <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>C</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><msub><mi>C</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">C_1,C_2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8778em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0715em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0715em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>, it's additive in the bellow sense:</p>\n<div class=\"math math-display\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mo>∫</mo><mi>F</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mo>∫</mo><msub><mi>C</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></msub><mi>F</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mi>n</mi><mo>+</mo><msub><mo>∫</mo><msub><mi>C</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></msub><mi>F</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\int F\\cdot n = \\int_{C_1} F\\cdot n + \\int_{C_2} F\\cdot n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.2222em;vertical-align:-0.8622em;\"></span><span class=\"mop op-symbol large-op\" style=\"margin-right:0.44445em;position:relative;top:-0.0011em;\">∫</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.372em;vertical-align:-1.012em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\"><span class=\"mop op-symbol large-op\" style=\"margin-right:0.44445em;position:relative;top:-0.0011em;\">∫</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:-0.4336em;\"><span style=\"top:-1.7881em;margin-left:-0.4445em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3173em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.357em;margin-left:-0.0715em;margin-right:0.0714em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.5em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.143em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.012em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6667em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.372em;vertical-align:-1.012em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\"><span class=\"mop op-symbol large-op\" style=\"margin-right:0.44445em;position:relative;top:-0.0011em;\">∫</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:-0.4336em;\"><span style=\"top:-1.7881em;margin-